name: Date
description: Adjusted sale date based on the restaurant's closing hour (02:30 AM). Sales made after midnight but before closing are recorded under the previous day's date.

name: Timestamp
description: Exact date and time of the invoice generation without adjustments.

name: Invoice_No_
description: Represents the invoice on which an item is sold. Since this is an item-level report, invoice numbers repeat for each item in a sale. Additionally, invoice numbers are reused over time by the POS system, so they are not unique.

name: Payment_Type
description: Indicates the method of payment used for a sale. It includes options like Cash, Online, Card, and various third-party payment methods (e.g., Paytm, Zomato Pay, UPI, AMEX). It also includes partial and due payments.

name: Order_Type
description: Specifies how the order was placed-Dine In (eaten at the restaurant), Delivery (Parcel sent to the customer), or Pick Up (customer collects the order).

name: Area
description: Indicates where the order was taken or processed. It includes on-premise locations (e.g., Garden Table, BAR Table, Personal Dine-In Room), third-party platforms (e.g., Zomato, Swiggy), and fulfillment methods (e.g., Parcel, Home Delivery, Room Service, Party).

name: Item_Name
description: Specifies the name of the dish or item sold in the order.

name: Price
description: Represents the base price of the dish or item sold in the order.

name: Qty_
description: Represents the number of units of a dish or item sold in the order.

name: Sub_Total
description: Calculated as Quantity x Base Price for a specific item in an order, before discounts and taxes.

name: Discount
description: Represents the discount applied to an item in a specific order.

name: Tax
description: Represents the total tax applied to an item, including SGST, CGST, VAT, and Service Charge.

name: Final_Total
description: Represents the item's total price after applying all taxes and discounts.

name: Status
description: Indicates the order's outcome-Success (completed sale), Complimentary (given for free), or Cancelled (order voided).

name: Table_No_
description: Identifies the designated table at the restaurant where the item was served.

name: Server_Name
description: Represents the name of the staff member whose login credentials were used to process the order.

name: Covers
description: Represents the number of guests (PAX) at a table for a given invoice. Since this is an item-level report, the PAX value repeats for each item in the same invoice.

name: Category
description: Specifies the menu category to which an item belongs.

name: Phone
description: Represents the guest's phone number linked to a specific invoice ID for that day.

name: Name
description: Represents the guest's name associated with a specific invoice ID for that day.

name: Address
description: Represents the guest's address associated with a specific invoice ID for that day.

name: GST
description: Represents the GST number associated with the guest's business.

name: Assign_To
description: Indicates the captain responsible for receiving and managing the order.

name: CGST_Rate
description: Specifies the percentage of Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST) applied to the item.

name: CGST_Amount
description: Specifies the amount of Central Goods and Services Tax (CGST) applied to the item.

name: SGST_Rate
description: Specifies the percentage of State Goods and Services Tax (SGST) applied to the item.

name: SGST_Amount
description: Specifies the amount of State Goods and Services Tax (SGST) applied to the item.

name: VAT_Rate
description: Specifies the percentage of Value Added Tax (VAT) applied to the item.

name: VAT_Amount
description: Specifies the amount of Value Added Tax (VAT) applied to the item.

name: Service_Charge_Rate
description: Specifies the percentage of Service Charge applied to the item.

name: Service_Charge_Amount
description: Specifies the amount of Service Charge applied to the item.

name: Date_z
description: Represents the date and timestamp when the order was received from Zomato, as per the Zomato report.

name: Aggregator_Order_No_z
description: Represents the order number from the Zomato report. It is unique per invoice but repeats for each item since this is an item-level report.

name: PoS_Invoice_No_z
description: Contains the same Invoice Number as the Invoice No. field, as recorded in the Zomato report.

name: Order_From_z
description: Specifies the name of the aggregator from which the order was received, as per the Zomato report.

name: Outlet_Name_z
description: Specifies the name of the outlet where the order was received, as per the Zomato report.

name: Order_Type_z
description: Indicates the type of order from the Zomato report. It only contains 'Delivery', while other entries are null or empty.

name: Customer_Name_z
description: Represents the customer's name as recorded in the Zomato report.

name: Payment_Type_z
description: Specifies the payment method for the order in the Zomato report. It only contains 'Online' or remains null.

name: Delivery_status_z
description: Contains the delivery executive's name and phone number in the format 'Zomato - [Name] ([Phone Number])' if the order is from Zomato; otherwise, it is null.

name: Status_z
description: Indicates the status of the Zomato order, with values such as 'Delivered' or 'Cancelled'.

name: My_amount_z
description: Represents the total invoice amount for a specific invoice on that day. Since this is an item-level report, the value repeats for each item in the same invoice.

name: Aggregator_Discount_z
description: Represents the discount applied to the order as per the Zomato report.

name: Outlet_Discount_z
description: Represents the discount provided by the outlet, as recorded in the Zomato report.

name: Total_z
description: Represents the total invoice amount for a specific invoice on that day, generally matching My_Amount_z in most cases.

name: Reason_z
description: Specifies the reason for any order action related to Zomato orders, as recorded in the Zomato report.

name: Online_Tax_Calculated_z
description: Represents the total tax amount on a Zomato order, as recorded in the Zomato report.

name: GST_Paid_by_Ecommerce_z
description: Represents the total tax amount paid by Zomato for a specific invoice, as recorded in the Zomato report.

name: Restaurant_ID_z
description: Represents the unique restaurant ID where the Zomato order was received, as per the Zomato report.

name: Order_ID_z
description: Contains the same value as Aggregator_Order_No_z, representing the order number from the Zomato report.

name: Order_Status_z
description: Contains the same value as Status_z, indicating the status of the Zomato order.

name: Received_Time_z
description: The date and timestamp when the Zomato order was received, as per the Zomato report.

name: Accepted_Time_z
description: The date and timestamp when the Zomato order was accepted, as per the Zomato report.

name: Mark_Ready_Time_z
description: The date and timestamp when the Zomato order was marked ready, as per the Zomato report.

name: Rider_Arrival_Time_z
description: The date and timestamp when the delivery personnel arrived at the restaurant to pick up the Zomato order, as per the Zomato report.

name: Picked_up_Time_z
description: The date and timestamp when the Zomato order was picked up by the delivery personnel, as per the Zomato report.

name: Delivered_Time_z
description: The date and timestamp when the Zomato order was delivered, as per the Zomato report.

name: Cancelled_Time_z
description: The date and timestamp when the Zomato order was canceled, as per the Zomato report.

name: Customer_Name_s

name: Payment_Type_s

name: Aggregator_Discount_s

name: Reason_s
description: Specifies the reason for any order action related to Swiggy orders, as recorded in the Swiggy report.

name: Online_Tax_Calculated_s
description: Represents the total tax amount on a Swiggy order, as recorded in the Swiggy report.

name: GST_Paid_by_Ecommerce_s
description: Represents the total tax amount paid by Swiggy for a specific invoice, as recorded in the Swiggy report.

name: Order_Status_s

name: Received_Time_s
description: The date and timestamp when the Swiggy order was received, as per the Swiggy report.

name: Accepted_Time_s
description: The date and timestamp when the Swiggy order was accepted, as per the Swiggy report.

name: Mark_Ready_Time_s
description: The date and timestamp when the Swiggy order was marked ready, as per the Swiggy report.

name: Rider_Arrival_Time_s
description: The date and timestamp when the delivery personnel arrived at the restaurant to pick up the Swiggy order, as per the Swiggy report.

name: Picked_up_Time_s

name: Delivered_Time_s

name: Cancelled_Time_s

name: PAX
description: Represents the number of people for a given invoice. This custom-coded field captures the PAX count only once per order, ensuring no duplication despite item-level reporting.

name: Biller_BSR
description: The name of the individual logged in while generating the bill, as recorded in the bill settlement report.

name: First_Print_Date_BSR
description: The date and timestamp when the invoice was printed for the first time, as per the bill modification report.

name: Last_Settlement_Date_BSR
description: The date and timestamp when the invoice was last printed after modification, as per the bill modification report.

name: Duration__In_Minutes_BSR
description: The total time taken to settle the bill for a particular invoice, as per the bill settlement report.

name: Settled_By_BSR
description: Represents the name of the biller who settled the bill, as recorded in the bill settlement report.

name: area_co
description: Specifies the source of the order, such as Zomato, Swiggy, Dine-In, or Personal Dine-In Room, as recorded in the canceled order report.

name: order_cancel_reason_co
description: Specifies the reason for the cancellation of a particular order, as recorded in the canceled order report.

name: Cancelled_Invoice_Total_co
description: Represents the total invoice amount for a canceled order, as recorded in the canceled order report.

name: Discount_DSR
description: Specifies the type of discount applied to a particular invoice, as recorded in the discount summary report.

name: Reason_DSR
description: Specifies the reason for the discount applied to a particular invoice, as recorded in the discount summary report.

name: Food_Preparation_Time_Z
description: Represents the total food preparation time for a Zomato order. Since the report is at the item level, this value repeats for all items in the same invoice.

name: Food_Preparation_Time_S
description: Represents the total food preparation time for a Swiggy order. Since the report is at the item level, this value repeats for all items in the same invoice.

name: Zomato_Delivery_Time
description: Represents the total delivery time for a Zomato order. Since the report is at the item level, this value repeats for all items in the same invoice.

name: Swiggy_Delivery_Time
description: Represents the total delivery time for a Swiggy order. Since the report is at the item level, this value repeats for all items in the same invoice.

name: amount_from
description: Represents the original invoice amount before any modifications, as recorded in the order report after print modification report.

name: amount_to
description: Represents the invoice amount after modifications, as recorded in the order report after the print modification.

name: modified_by
description: Represents the name of the cashier who modified the invoice amount, as recorded in the order report after the print modification.

name: modify_comment
description: Provides the reason for the invoice modification, as recorded in the order report after the print modification.

name: electron_pos
description: Represents the date and timestamp when the invoice was modified, as recorded in the order report after the print modification.

name: invoice_no
description: represents the invoice number if it was modified; otherwise, it remains null, as recorded in the order report after the print modification.
